THE GUT BOUNDARY CONDITION (Level 1)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

  At M_GUT in SU(5): 1/alpha_1 = 1/alpha_2 = 1/alpha_GUT
  1/alpha_EM = (5/3)/alpha_1 + 1/alpha_2 = (8/3)/alpha_GUT
  sin^2(theta_W) = (1/alpha_GUT) / ((8/3)/alpha_GUT) = 3/8

  sin^2(theta_W) at M_GUT (dimensionless)  0.375

